  83:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** /*
  84:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** @Note: This interface is implemented to operate in zero-copy mode only:
  85:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****         - Rx Buffers will be allocated from LwIP stack Rx memory pool,
  86:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****           then passed to ETH HAL driver.
  87:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****         - Tx Buffers will be allocated from LwIP stack memory heap,
  88:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****           then passed to ETH HAL driver.
ARM GAS  C:\Users\hh\AppData\Local\Temp\ccCKtegN.s 			page 3


  89:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** 
  90:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** @Notes:
  91:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   1.a. ETH DMA Rx descriptors must be contiguous, the default count is 4,
  92:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        to customize it please redefine ETH_RX_DESC_CNT in ETH GUI (Rx Descriptor Length)
  93:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        so that updated value will be generated in stm32xxxx_hal_conf.h
  94:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   1.b. ETH DMA Tx descriptors must be contiguous, the default count is 4,
  95:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        to customize it please redefine ETH_TX_DESC_CNT in ETH GUI (Tx Descriptor Length)
  96:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        so that updated value will be generated in stm32xxxx_hal_conf.h
  97:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** 
  98:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   2.a. Rx Buffers number must be between ETH_RX_DESC_CNT and 2*ETH_RX_DESC_CNT
  99:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   2.b. Rx Buffers must have the same size: ETH_RX_BUFFER_SIZE, this value must
 100:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        passed to ETH DMA in the init field (heth.Init.RxBuffLen)
 101:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   2.c  The RX Ruffers addresses and sizes must be properly defined to be aligned
 102:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        to L1-CACHE line size (32 bytes).
 103:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** */
 104:LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** 
